                <h1></h1>
                <p>Plastic pollution poses a significant threat to our planet, infiltrating oceans, waterways, and landscapes. Millions of tons of plastic waste harm wildlife, ecosystems, and human health. Reducing plastic use, promoting recycling, and supporting sustainable alternatives are essential steps in combating this growing crisis and protecting our environment.</p>
